Reasoning: The paper discusses the challenges of semantic parsing in solving mathematical word problems, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also covers automatic solvers for geometric problems that require the understanding of diagrams, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the performance of different techniques on publicly accessible datasets, which falls under data science (cs.DS).
